metadata.description:
Good Society 005: chromonicci - Me.

chromonicci is an artist that needs little introduction. He's carved a completely unique lane for himself; creating distinct pockets of hip hop, electronic, R&B, & more which are all tied together by his signature niccibounce production and lush vocal harmonies. His catalog is equally large as it is diverse with each song being recognizably him.

Our story with nicci dates back to the beginnings of Good Society from having booked him for our first live shows, to releasing multiple songs, a slew of music related adventures, and countless philosophical conversations.

"This song represents a point of growth I can look back at and hold nothing but love for the person I am today. Thank you for engaging with my work, and I hope you enjoy.

With Love,
Chromonicci"
